### Get Kandang Asisten by Kandang (Original Endpoint)
GET https://localhost:7195/api/kandang-asistens/by-kandang/fd082b84-41c8-45d4-8480-ddb918f74cca
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Kandang Asisten by Kandang WITH Ayam Sisa Information (NEW ENDPOINT)
GET https://localhost:7195/api/kandang-asistens/by-kandang/fd082b84-41c8-45d4-8480-ddb918f74cca/with-ayam-sisa
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Kandang Asisten by Kandang (Active Only)
GET https://localhost:7195/api/kandang-asistens/by-kandang/fd082b84-41c8-45d4-8480-ddb918f74cca/active
Accept: application/json

